{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/accelerated-capability-environment/about","content_id":"cb39a4dd-1c50-41ac-9c59-ff398304b461","description":"ACE is a Home Office unit that takes a highly innovative approach to solving public sector technology and data challenges. Contact us at ace@homeoffice.gov.uk","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Home Office-owned Accelerated Capability Environment (<abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr>) is a public private partnership that tackles complex problems facing government, delivering mission impact at pace.</p>\n\n<p>It has delivered more than 700 commissions for 50+ public sector organisations since 2017, often finding a data or tech driven solution.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr> has created a space where the best talents from government, industry and academia can collaborate, experiment and solve public sector problems fast, embracing the entrepreneurial and agile behaviours of a start-up.</p>\n\n<p>To do this, it draws on the <abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr> community, which comprises hundreds of companies, largely SMEs, and a substantial Academic Research Network (<abbr title=\"Academic Research Network\">ARN</abbr>), made up of individual academics as well as institutions. These provide government with instant access to expert capabilities while supporting the growth of small businesses.</p>\n\n<p>Some of the ways <abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr> can support you:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Problem definition:</strong> if a problem has a clear, ready-built solution, it’s not for <abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr>. But if it requires defining, testing and iteration, we are here to help navigate the unknown.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Rapid identification and development of solutions:</strong> the pace at which we work is genuinely surprising, typically delivering an outcome within 12 weeks.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Access to our community and <abbr title=\"Academic Research Network\">ARN</abbr>:</strong> unlike traditional procurement processes, we bring together ‘rainbow teams’ where industry and academia, who might never normally work together, collaborate to find a solution to a problem.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>De-risking innovation and procurement:</strong> <abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr>’s delivery experts help to explore, test and refine solutions, making sure it’s the right answer for your problem.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Upskill your teams:</strong> by working alongside <abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr> and our suppliers, your teams will learn how to innovate while retaining full control of the process.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Future and insights expertise:</strong> stay ahead of emerging trends with intelligence from our dedicated future and insights market team.</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Enabling services:</strong> these include secure data environments and collaborative office spaces where our teams can work together.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Accelerated Capability Environment\">ACE</abbr> can tackle almost any problem. Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:ace@homeoffice.gov.uk\">ace@homeoffice.gov.uk</a> to find out how we can help your team or to find out more about our work.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2022-11-14T11:29:17Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["eeb13b1a-cf98-42e1-b46d-fa3cc4a9a172"],"name":"Access our information"}],"organisation":"92bbe2da-8d5f-480b-8da1-50b18e317654","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2022-11-14T11:29:17+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/accelerated-capability-environment/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/governmen